companyName: Invesco MSCI Emerging Markets Equal Country Weight
description:
The investment seeks to correspond, before fees and expenses, to the price and yield performance of the MSCI Emerging Markets Equal Country Weighted Index (the "underlying index").
 The fund invests primarily in equity securities to meet its investment objective of corresponding to the underlying index as closely as possible, before fees and expenses. The MSCI Emerging Markets Index is a free float-adjusted market capitalization index that is designed to measure equity market performance of certain markets deemed to be emerging markets. The fund is non-diversified.
